CREATE USER IF NOT EXISTS "SA" SALT '18b1db73d832984b' HASH 'ea4358312474d66acd71d80e88e303641a6193fed7c29dbebd24d7994c4ab26e' ADMIN;         
CREATE MEMORY TABLE "PUBLIC"."CONCERTS"(
    "BOUGHT_MERCH" BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    "CROWD_ENERGY_SCORE" INTEGER,
    "DANCED_ALL_NIGHT" BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    "DATE_ATTENDED" DATE NOT NULL,
    "DURATION_MINUTES" INTEGER,
    "ENCORE_COUNT" INTEGER,
    "FIRST_TIME_SEEN" BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    "MERCH_SPENT_EUR" NUMERIC(10, 2),
    "PHONE_FREE_SHOW" BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    "PRODUCTION_SCORE" INTEGER,
    "RATING" INTEGER,
    "SETLIST_SCORE" INTEGER,
    "SONGS_PLAYED" INTEGER,
    "TEAR_JERKER" BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    "TICKET_PRICE_EUR" NUMERIC(10, 2),
    "TRAVEL_COST_EUR" NUMERIC(10, 2),
    "VIBE_SCORE" INTEGER,
    "VOCAL_FORM_SCORE" INTEGER,
    "ADDED_BY_ID" BIGINT,
    "CREATED_AT" TIMESTAMP(6),
    "ID" BIGINT GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY(START WITH 1 RESTART WITH 11) NOT NULL,
    "UPDATED_AT" TIMESTAMP(6),
    "CITY" CHARACTER VARYING(100) NOT NULL,
    "COUNTRY" CHARACTER VARYING(100),
    "CREW_WITH" CHARACTER VARYING(200),
    "FAVORITE_SONG" CHARACTER VARYING(200),
    "MAIN_ARTIST" CHARACTER VARYING(200) NOT NULL,
    "MOOD_TAGS" CHARACTER VARYING(200),
    "TOUR_NAME" CHARACTER VARYING(200),
    "VENUE" CHARACTER VARYING(200) NOT NULL,
    "OPENING_ACTS" CHARACTER VARYING(300),
    "BEST_MOMENT" CHARACTER VARYING(500),
    "PERSONAL_NOTES" CHARACTER VARYING(2000),
    "SETLIST_NOTES" CHARACTER VARYING(2000),
    "GENRE" ENUM('ALT_ROCK', 'BEDROOM_POP', 'ELECTRONIC', 'EMO_REVIVAL', 'FOLK', 'HIP_HOP', 'HOUSE', 'HYPERPOP', 'INDIE_POP', 'INDIE_ROCK', 'JAZZ', 'JPOP', 'KPOP', 'METAL', 'POP', 'PUNK', 'RAP', 'RNB', 'ROCK', 'SHOEGAZE', 'SOUL', 'TECHNO') NOT NULL,
    "SECONDARY_GENRE" ENUM('ALT_ROCK', 'BEDROOM_POP', 'ELECTRONIC', 'EMO_REVIVAL', 'FOLK', 'HIP_HOP', 'HOUSE', 'HYPERPOP', 'INDIE_POP', 'INDIE_ROCK', 'JAZZ', 'JPOP', 'KPOP', 'METAL', 'POP', 'PUNK', 'RAP', 'RNB', 'ROCK', 'SHOEGAZE', 'SOUL', 'TECHNO'),
    "SHOW_TYPE" ENUM('ACOUSTIC_SET', 'AMPHITHEATER', 'ARENA_TOUR', 'CLUB_SHOW', 'FESTIVAL_SET', 'INTIMATE_VENUE', 'OUTDOOR_FREE', 'RESIDENCY', 'SECRET_SHOW', 'STADIUM_TOUR') NOT NULL,
    "VENUE_SIZE" ENUM('AMPHITHEATER', 'ARENA', 'DIVE_BAR', 'FESTIVAL_FIELD', 'LARGE_VENUE', 'MID_VENUE', 'SMALL_CLUB', 'STADIUM'),
    "VIEWING_AREA" ENUM('BALCONY', 'BARRICADE', 'FESTIVAL_FIELD', 'FRONT_PIT', 'GENERAL_ADMISSION', 'SEATED_FLOOR', 'SEATED_LOWER', 'SEATED_UPPER', 'STANDING_ONLY', 'VIP_BOX')
);     
